activities.activityName: Go for a walk with a book that you won't read
outcomes: I got interviewed by a TikToker and the Internet made fun of me :(
I didn't remember to take out the book of my tote bag, but someone gifted me a massage coupon!!
A cute person sat next to me and asked for books recommendations... and my number!!!
I tried doing the Astavakrasana but my hand slipped and it hurt so much :,(
I believe I reached the Nirvana and now I don't have problems sleeeping!!!
I became intimate with the modern moms and they gifted me a pricey necklace!
The treadmill outruned me and I fell in a ridiculous way to the floor :(
The gym was empty and I could blast out loud Taylor Swift without any judgement from the gymbros
I lifted more weight than the noisy gymbro and make him cry!!!!!!!
There was nothing cute of my size and I started crying in the middle of the shopping center
I exited one shop without paying and nobody noticed... oops!
Everything I wanted was half-priced and I even got gifted a curious book!!
I was crying so bad watching Lorelai and Rory love each other so much that the pizza on the oven got burn
I wanted to be like Rory so you read an intellectual book in one sitting
I got moved so much by the relation of Emily and Lorelai that I called my mother to ask how is her life
I mistook my glass of wine and drank the dirty water instead... IT WAS HORRIBLE!
I ended with my hands lilac, stained the t-shirt of the person next to me without them knowing and ran away with it!!
The hot teacher was impressed by my painting and went down their knees to ask me on a date!!!
I got distracted learning a choreography, and burnt the cookies in the oven :(
I got the quantities wrong, so now I got cookies for a whole week!
My cute and silly neighbour smelt my cookies and I invited them to stay the night...
Never in my life have I been surrounded by so many monkey dudes that I had to ran away crying!!
I unplugged the mixing desk while nobody was watching and use the distraction to fill my pockets with the telephones of the annoying dudes... oops!
I got everyone to burn down the dance floor to the beat of Sophie!! I was born to do this!
I had to fought a spider's nest and couldn't end cleaning :( IT WAS HORRIBLE!
I got distracted while cleaning with things I didn't remember having and found money under the bed!
I feel life is worth living again, everything is in order and so is my life!

activities.activityName: Call mom and listen to her complains
outcomes: We ended up yelling at each other because of a misunderstanding!! HATE HER!!
I left the telephone in the room while I showered and when I went back she was still talking alone... sorry not sorry!
I realised I have grown old just as my mother, and although she is guilty of part of my pain, I understand her...

activities.activityName: Write fanfics with the lights off
outcomes: A screenshot of my fic went viral on Twitter and everybody made fun of me!!
The omegaverse fans praised my fic and made me an internet sensation... Yuhu! I guess?
'The Lovely Adventures of Paquita and Fernandito' became an internet sensation and they offered me a publishing contract!!

activities.activityName: Go vintage shopping with a cute hat
outcomes: Nobody complemented my avant garde hat and I bought a scabies dress without knowing! WORST EXPERIENCE EVER!
I found the perfect skirt to match my extravagant hat! Life is worth living!
An alternative hot looking person complemented my outfit and asked for my number!!!
The neighbours heard my laments and called the police to see if something was wrong... EMBARRASSING!!
I cried in silence all night long and wake up refreshed and thinking life is about the ups and the downs
I tweeted how much I liked a certain sad singer song, and they replied and asked me on a date! Feeling like Paul Mescal rn...
My friends were #TeamJacob (ew), so I fought with them! They are never entering my house till they rethink it!
I dreamt a hot vampire lured me into the dark and now I wait every night by the window...
We all bonded talking and dreaming about Edward Cullen (Edward, if you ever read this, call me up!!)
My legs hurt so much that I had to exit crawling!!!
I bonded with the lonely ladies in the corner and started dancing together till the floor fell down!!!
I fell off the horse straight into the strong arms of a cowboy and ride all night long... yeah!
